cross: Alantuckerara Cedar Creek x Galeopetalum Black Knight

measurements.description: Nine flowers on two inflorescences to 40cm long; sepals and petals green heavily suffused maroon to appear dense bronze; lip white, flushed and veined bright purple, crest light lavender; column green fully overlaid black basally, mottled at tip, anther cap green; substance firm; texture matte.
